# ==============================================================================
# RustApps main .gitignore
# This file provides global ignore rules
# ==============================================================================

### --- Rust / Cargo ---
# Ignore the build output directory for every sub-project
**/target/

# Ignore backup files created by cargo-fix or other tools
**/*.rs.bk

### --- Environment & Secrets ---
# Ignore local environment variables (where you might store API keys)
.env
.env.*
! .env.example

### --- IDEs & Editors ---
# JetBrains (IntelliJ, RustRover, CLion, etc.)
**/.idea/
*.iml

# Visual Studio Code
**/.vscode/
# Note: You might want to allow sharing some VSCode configs:
# !**/.vscode/settings.json
# !**/.vscode/tasks.json
# !**/.vscode/launch.json

# Vim / Emacs
*~
*.swp
*.swo
[._]*.s[a-v][a-z]

### --- OS Generated Files ---
# macOS
.DS_Store
.AppleDouble
.LSOverride

# Windows
Thumbs.db
ehthumbs.db
Desktop.ini

### --- Testing & Profiling ---
# Code coverage reports (e.g., from tarpaulin or kcov)
**/target/debug/coverage/
*.profraw
tarpaulin-report.html

